      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED HOT BERNIE (7) boasts a consistent overall record including 14 wins from 32 starts, the latest winning (16.91) over 300m at Mandurah. Form here is sound including seven wins. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. CLEARY KEEPING (3) was in hot form, winning two on end before colliding in the run last time and finishing eighth in a Grade 3/4 at Mandurah (18.06). Gets chance to atone. CRACKERJACK SCUD (8) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Mandurah over 400m behind Zatara's Image (23.10) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. Can do much better this time. DANCING DENNIS (2) was in the money last start and poses a threat again.",
